entries.title_d: Travel to the Dathomir system and destroy the Rebels. Some Rebel pilots tried to gain access to Dathomir by using a fake authorization code, but they made the mistake of celebrating while their comm channel was still open. Teach them a lesson.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Destroy the Impertinent Rebels
entries.taunt_4: You should have stayed at home hiding under your mother's skirt.
entries.taunt_3: Time to take out the trash...by the way, you are the trash.
entries.taunt_2: Nice move, but you will have to do much better in order to win.
entries.taunt_1: Foolish Imperial! You are no match for me.
entries.targets_detected: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:\#pcontrast3 <Enemy fighters incoming at attack speeds. Prepare to engage.>
entries.targets_behind: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:\#pcontrast3 <Alert! Enemy fighters incoming from behind at high speeds.>
entries.quest_location_d: Some Rebel pilots tried to gain access to Dathomir by using a fake authorization code, but they made the mistake of celebrating while their comm channel was still open. Teach them a lesson.
entries.quest_destroy_d: Some Rebel pilots tried to gain access to Dathomir by using a fake authorization code, but they made the mistake of celebrating while their comm channel was still open. Teach them a lesson.
entries.quest_d: Some Rebel pilots tried to gain access to Dathomir by using a fake authorization code, but they made the mistake of celebrating while their comm channel was still open. Teach them a lesson.
entries.level_increase: You have done well, but that was just the beginning. The better pilots are still to come.
entries.level_boss_dead: Nice work but remember there is still more work to be done. Stand by for location of next target.
entries.level_boss: \#pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:\#pcontrast3 <%TO has been eliminated. The Rebels in this region are leaderless.>
entries.found_loc: We have located more pirates that need to be driven out of this system. Travel to the location provided to your nav computer and eliminate the Rebels.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_5: You have caused enough trouble. It is time for me to end this.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_4: Time to teach this Imperial whelp who really rules Dathomir.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_3: You had better be gone before I taunt you a second time.
entries.dd_boss_taunt_2: You are the pilot that they sent against me? HA!
entries.dd_boss_taunt_1: Prepare to be left to the mercys of cold, empty space.
entries.complete: Nice flying out there, pilot. You are really turning into an elite pilot. Return to your commander and report your success.
entries.boss_detected: Be on the look out. A Rebel Gunboat has been detected in your region.
